    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the point of any of this. like if you look at the scale of the universe, everything we do is just a tiny flicker before the heat death of everything. why bother struggling or building anything when it's all just going to be cold and empty anyway? it feels like we're just running on a treadmill to nowhere.",
