      "content": "but that's just a romantic way of glorifying suffering. you're basically saying existence is only \"valuable\" because it's fleeting, but that doesn't change the fact that the pain is real and the nothingness is certain. if the universe is indifferent, then my suffering is just an unnecessary glitch in the system. wouldn't it be more rational to just opt out while you still have some control, rather than being forced into an inevitable end by entropy?",
